<Title>Nose Gear Landing and Taxi Lights</Title>
<DispatchCondition>
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>Any number may be missing provided wiring is disconnected, capped and stowed. For each missing light lens, open the appropriate circuit breaker using a flight deck multi-function display and lock with an INOP tag.  The associated landing light or taxi light must be considered inoperative.</Para>
<Note>
<Para>The airplane must be dispatched using MEL item 33-42-01.</Para>
</Note>
